          content:`Clinical AI risk assessment. Patient: ${patient.name}, age ${patient.age}. Conditions: ${patient.conditions.join(", ")}. Glucose avg 148, BP 140/89, HbA1c 7.4%, LDL 118, eGFR 72, Weight 181 trending down. Adherence 78%. Write in plain English a non-technical patient can understand. Respond ONLY raw JSON:
{"overall_risk":"moderate","risk_score":62,"risk_trend":"improving","summary":"2 sentences in simple English explaining overall health status","cardiovascular":{"level":"high","score":72,"plain_english":"One sentence a patient can understand"},"diabetes":{"level":"moderate","score":58,"plain_english":"One sentence a patient can understand"},"kidney":{"level":"low","score":28,"plain_english":"One sentence a patient can understand"},"top_3_actions":["Simple action 1","Simple action 2","Simple action 3"],"good_news":["positive thing 1","positive thing 2","positive thing 3"],"when_to_call_doctor":"One clear sentence about when to call"}`}]})});
